"attention."

#: src/Gateway/CashuGateway.php:432
msgid ""
"We couldn't reach the Cashu mint right now. Please reload to try again, or "
"contact the store if this keeps happening."
msgstr ""
"Impossible de joindre le mint Cashu pour le moment. Veuillez recharger pour "
"réessayer, ou contacter la boutique si le problème persiste."

#: src/Gateway/CashuGateway.php:436
